Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.02,0:34:23.20,English,,0,0,0,,And so we're living in rat utopia.\N{\rChinese}于是我们住在老鼠的乌托邦。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.40,0:34:24.72,English,,0,0,0,,And quite honestly,\N{\rChinese}而且说实话，
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.92,0:34:30.00,English,,0,0,0,,this is why young people now refuse to have children.\N{\rChinese}这就是年轻人现在不愿意生孩子的原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.10,0:34:31.46,English,,0,0,0,,It's not just because\N{\rChinese}这不只是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.46,0:34:35.80,English,,0,0,0,,the economic opportunities for young people are very limited,\N{\rChinese}年轻人的经济机会非常有限
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.88,0:34:39.18,English,,0,0,0,,are very pessimistic, and they are.\N{\rChinese}很悲观，且确实如此。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.34,0:34:43.98,English,,0,0,0,,The real reason is the baby boomers refuse to give up their status.\N{\rChinese}真正原因是婴儿潮人不愿放弃其地位。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.24,0:34:48.26,English,,0,0,0,,Think about the politicians in Washington DC.\N{\rChinese}想想华盛顿特区的政客们。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.98,0:34:53.48,English,,0,0,0,,I mean like many of them,\N{\rChinese}我说的是像他们中的许多人。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.60,0:34:56.34,English,,0,0,0,,their brains aren't even functioning and they're still there.\N{\rChinese}他们的大脑还没运转，却还在场上。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.68,0:35:02.68,English,,0,0,0,,And so we live in a time of rat utopia.\N{\rChinese}于是我们生活在鼠国乌托邦的时代。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.82,0:35:06.10,English,,0,0,0,,But again, these people are the ones\N{\rChinese}但又是这些人，
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.10,0:35:09.00,English,,0,0,0,,who gave us birth, the ones who nurtured us, the ones\N{\rChinese}他们给了我们生命，抚育了我们，
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.00,0:35:10.96,English,,0,0,0,,who we must honor and cherish.\N{\rChinese}我们必须敬仰并珍爱他们。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.20,0:35:14.80,English,,0,0,0,,So we can never ever blame the baby boomers for what's going on.\N{\rChinese}于是我们永远不会把正在发生的事归咎给婴儿潮人。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.88,0:35:18.58,English,,0,0,0,,We blame the immigrants, or we blame the Jews, or we blame the steep state,\N{\rChinese}我们把责任推给移民，或者推给犹太人，或者推给民族国家，或者推给特朗普，或者推给特鲁多。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.70,0:35:20.38,English,,0,0,0,,or we blame Trump, or we blame Justin Trudeau.\N{\rChinese}or we blame Trump, or we blame Justin Trudeau.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.44,0:35:23.74,English,,0,0,0,,We never blame the real culprits who are the baby boomers.\N{\rChinese}我们从未曾把真正的罪魇归咎给婴儿潮人。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.94,0:35:26.04,English,,0,0,0,,So the question then is, what can we do?\N{\rChinese}于是问题是，我们能做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.56,0:35:30.48,English,,0,0,0,,And so I think the only thing we can do is tell the truth.\N{\rChinese}我认为我们能做的唯一事就是说出真相。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.84,0:35:32.28,English,,0,0,0,,We owe it to ourselves,\N{\rChinese}我们欠自己的，
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.54,0:35:35.98,English,,0,0,0,,we owe it to our children to let them know the truth.\N{\rChinese}我们欠我们的孩子，让他们知道真相。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.18,0:35:38.72,English,,0,0,0,,It was not the immigrants who destroyed the West,\N{\rChinese}不是移民毁了西方。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.92,0:35:42.36,English,,0,0,0,,it was not Putin or Trump or Trudeau who gave up their status.\N{\rChinese}它不是普京、特朗普或特鲁多放弃了他们的地位。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.36,0:35:45.60,English,,0,0,0,,Nobody can take it away from them. Nobody can take it away from them. who destroyed the West.\N{\rChinese}谁能把它从他们手里夺走？谁能把它从他们手里夺走。谁毁了西方。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.92,0:35:48.48,English,,0,0,0,,It was not the Jews. It was us.\N{\rChinese}不是犹太人。是我们。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.92,0:35:51.72,English,,0,0,0,,Because we became selfish,\N{\rChinese}因为我们变得自私，懒散，腐败。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.02,0:35:54.70,English,,0,0,0,,lazy, and corrupt.\N{\rChinese}那才是西方衰亡的真正原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.94,0:35:58.12,English,,0,0,0,,That's the real reason why the West is dying\N{\rChinese}That's the real reasonwhy the West is dying
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.12,0:36:01.46,English,,0,0,0,,and the real reason why no one can do anything about it.\N{\rChinese}以及真正原因，谁也做不到什么事。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.68,0:36:07.64,English,,0,0,0,,Because we refuse to admit the truth to ourselves.\N{\rChinese}因为我们不肯自认真相。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.64,0:36:13.12,English,,0,0,0,,But the least we can do is tell the truth to our children.\N{\rChinese}但至少我们可以把真相告诉我们的孩子。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.28,0:36:16.90,English,,0,0,0,,And that's why I do what I do.\N{\rChinese}于是我才会这么做。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.46,0:36:20.70,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so again,\N{\rChinese}好了，再说一次，
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.94,0:36:24.36,English,,0,0,0,,apologies for today.\N{\rChinese}今天先说声抱歉。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.48,0:36:26.24,English,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it's such doom and gloom.\N{\rChinese}很抱歉，真是这么沧落的气氛。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.46,0:36:31.66,English,,0,0,0,,Next week, we go back to the regular programming of just cheer.\N{\rChinese}下周我们回到常规的节目，继续欢喜。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.68,0:36:36.88,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, no, I'm not going to ever be optimistic about the world\N{\rChinese}好了，我再也不再对世界抱有乐观。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.88,0:36:38.62,English,,0,0,0,,because there's no way I'm going to be optimistic about the world. There's no reason to be optimistic about the world.\N{\rChinese}因为我再也不再对世界抱有乐观。没有理由再乐观。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.98,0:36:42.00,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so next week, I'm going to preview\N{\rChinese}好了，接下来一周，我要预览。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.62,0:36:46.12,English,,0,0,0,,the next academic year of classes I'll be teaching.\N{\rChinese}接下来一学年我将要授课的课程。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.22,0:36:50.64,English,,0,0,0,,I'll be teaching three new classes, The Secret History of the World.\N{\rChinese}我将开设三门新课， 《世界的秘密历史》。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.80,0:36:54.56,English,,0,0,0,,So I'll be going into the nexus of finance, intelligence, and religion.\N{\rChinese}我将深入探讨金融、情报与宗教的交汇点。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.86,0:36:57.74,English,,0,0,0,,It's going to be a really interesting class. I'm really looking forward to teaching it.\N{\rChinese}这将是一门非常有趣的课程，我已迫不及待去授课。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.84,0:36:59.68,English,,0,0,0,,I'm really looking forward to sharing with you.\N{\rChinese}我很期待与大家分享。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.78,0:37:01.04,English,,0,0,0,,I'll also be teaching the great books.\N{\rChinese}我还将讲授经典著作。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.10,0:37:03.20,English,,0,0,0,,I'll also be teaching game theory.\N{\rChinese}我还会讲授博弈论。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.32,0:37:06.92,English,,0,0,0,,So in my next video next week, I'll be sharing with you, previewing,\N{\rChinese}于是在下周的下一期视频里，我会先跟你们预览，然后再跟你们分享这三门课程。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.62,0:37:09.86,English,,0,0,0,,and then I'll be sharing with you these three classes.\N{\rChinese}如果你喜欢我的工作，...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.76,0:37:13.34,English,,0,0,0,,If you like what I do,\N{\rChinese}If you like whatI do,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.48,0:37:18.06,English,,0,0,0,,please support my work by supporting me on Buy Me a Coffee.\N{\rChinese}请在Buy Me a Coffee上支持我的工作。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.20,0:37:19.70,English,,0,0,0,,The link is below.\N{\rChinese}链接在下方。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.76,0:37:24.16,English,,0,0,0,,If you want to be part of my community,\N{\rChinese}如果你想加入我的社区，
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.32,0:37:27.96,English,,0,0,0,,the Breakdown History community, please join my Discord server.\N{\rChinese}分解历史社区，请加入我的 Discord 服务器。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.68,0:37:31.60,English,,0,0,0,,This week, I've started a sub stack.\N{\rChinese}本周，我已启动了一个子堆栈。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.78,0:37:34.66,English,,0,0,0,,And if you want to join my sub stack,\N{\rChinese}如果你想加入我的子堆栈，
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.76,0:37:37.16,English,,0,0,0,,the link is below.\N{\rChinese}链接在下方。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.66,0:37:40.36,English,,0,0,0,,So in my sub stack,\N{\rChinese}于是在我的子堆栈中，
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.58,0:37:43.96,English,,0,0,0,,I'll be going into\N{\rChinese}我将进入
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.96,0:37:48.56,English,,0,0,0,,solutions for how we can rebuild a better world.\N{\rChinese}解决方案，让我们能重建更好的世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.64,0:37:53.56,English,,0,0,0,,How we can work together to build a better world after the world collapses.\N{\rChinese}我们如何合作，在世界崩溃后建造更好的世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.10,0:37:56.76,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's it for today.\N{\rChinese}好了，今天就到此为止。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.98,0:37:58.30,English,,0,0,0,,I'll see you guys next week.\N{\rChinese}我下周见你们。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.44,0:38:01.02,English,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for today.\N{\rChinese}今天非常感谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.22,0:38:03.80,English,,0,0,0,,And I look forward to next week.\N{\rChinese}我期待下周。
